                            <li><i class="fas fa-clock text-blue-500 mr-2"></i><strong>Level 2 :</strong> 88 questions, formats mixtes</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-clock text-blue-500 mr-2"></i><strong>Level 3 :</strong> Essays + QCM, gestion complexe</li>
